com.paypal.selion.grid.servlets.transfer

Interface ServerRepository

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ManagedArtifactRepository

    public interface ServerRepository
    ServerRepository represents a repository for storing any artifacts of type ManagedArtifact received by HTTP POST upload request. The artifacts are saved and returned as a type extending ManagedArtifact which the implementations are free to implement.
